posting_body: ['Welcome to 1825 Mission Apartments', 'Welcome to a new standard of apartment home living at 1825 Mission.', 'Our community is situated in San Francisco, California.', 'Our location in the Mission District places you just minutes from a fantastic selection of restaurants, shopping, and entertainment options.', 'The heart of the city is at your doorstep with easy access to BART, MUNI, and Interstate 101.', 'Experience the exciting opportunities San Francisco has to offer at 1825 Mission.', 'Apartment Features:', 'Granite Countertops', 'Microwave', 'Newly Renovated Interiors', 'Refrigerator', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Views Available', 'Community Features:', 'Parking Available', 'Part-time Courtesy Patrol', 'Picnic Area with Barbecue', 'Public Parks Nearby', 'State-of-the-art Fitness Center', 'Theater Room', 'Pet Policy', 'Looking for a pet-friendly apartment community in San Francisco, CA?', 'Look no further than 1825 Mission!', 'As a pet-friendly community, we proudly allow cats and dogs here at 1825 Mission.', 'Now your pet can relax by your side and enjoy the comforts of your apartment home.', 'Pets Welcome Upon Approval.', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
